content.html: I love this image. Saturn's moon Mimas, hanging in space in front of the giant planet's northern hemisphere. The bands across the planet are the shadows of Saturn's rings, which make an appearance at the bottom of the scene.
content.value:
I love this image.

Saturn's moon Mimas, hanging in space in front of the giant planet's northern hemisphere.

The bands across the planet are the shadows of Saturn's rings, which make an appearance at the bottom of the scene.
